txt.en: 'I was attacked by some of her hatchlings and wounded, though none of them survived to report to their mother.'
'If you take my torch, you might be able to burn the cocoons and webs, preventing anymore of her spawn from coming to her aid.'
'I will keep torches lit for you. Hurry! Slay the foul beast and her spawn! Be wary, though... stay upon the thicker strands, lest you perish!'
'Prepare to join the ranks of Dol Guldur's Dead!'
'Ah, you have come... whoever you are....'
'Come, brethren, feed the fires! Call the Dead!'
'Who dares intrude upon the lands of the Necromancer?'
'I found the queen of the spiders... a creature like none I have ever seen.'
